The paper deals with image understanding and natural language processing, which are both subfields of computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also discusses learning approaches and generalization, which are topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper proposes a benchmark for image captioning, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR).
